Version 0.1.3, 2010.09.09

* Pass additional arguments to `Arcadia#addControls` through to the control
  constructor.
* Add an `options` argument to the `Arcadia.Controls.Play` constructor.
* Allow the selection of the direction of travel caused by
  `Arcadia.Controls.Play`; it can be either `previous` or `next`.

Version 0.1.2, 2010.09.09

* Added a decent README.
* Descriptions passed to the gallery constructor can now be JSON strings, not
  just objects.

Version 0.1.1, 2010.05.18

* Empty descriptions shouldn't be displayed.
* Fixed an insertion order bug.
* When creating a gallery, centre on the first item in the collection.

Version 0.1.0, 2010.04.15

* Initial release.
